1. *Pravim* salatu za večeru. (I'm making a salad for dinner.)
2. *Pravi* se da je sve u redu. (He is pretending that everything is ok.)
3. *Praviću* joj poklon za rođendan. (I'm going to make her a present for her birthday.)
4. Ona *pravi* probleme sa svojim roditeljima. (She is having problems with her parents.) 
5. *Pravio* sam svoju stranicu na internetu. (I was making my website on the internet.) 
6. *Pravljenje* vina je dug i složen proces. (Making wine is a long and complex process.)